Taylor, Andrew Brookins, Catherine Graham, Robert Bailey, Evelyn Young, Isaac Willoughby, Christine Jones, Jack Fisher, Oplenell Rockamore, Clarence Payne, and Helen Thompson, gathered in Central Baptist Church for baby shower, another version
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 22, 1964, pg. 15 reads: "Central Board Showers Leader - Members of the Board of Education of Central Baptist Church (pictured above) were hosts to a Baby Shower, recently, in honor of the new arrival at the home of their director, Mrs. Edith Venable (seated, second from left). Among those who participated in the occasion held at the church (seated, left to right) are Mrs. Josephine Moore, Mrs. Venable, Rev. W. Augustus Jones, Mrs. Isaac Green, wife of the pastor, and Mrs. Bell Lunn.  Standing, left to right, A.D. Taylor, Andrew Brookins, Mrs. Catherine Graham, Robert Bailey, Mrs. Evelyn Young, Isaac Willoughby, Mrs. Christine Jones, Jack Fisher, Mrs. Oplenell Rockamore, Clarence Payne and Mrs. Helen Thompson. - Harris Photo."
